+#### Enabling CSS formatting within `<mj-style>` tag (#17338 by @iryusa)
+
+<!-- prettier-ignore -->
+```mjml
+<!-- Input -->
+<mj-style>
+.hello {
+  color: blue;
+    border: 1px solid blue;
+font-size:12px;
+} p { font-size: 14px; }
+</mj-style>
+
+<!-- Prettier stable -->
+<mj-style>
+  .hello { color: blue; border: 1px solid blue; font-size:12px; } p { font-size:
+  14px; }
+</mj-style>
+
+<!-- Prettier main -->
+<mj-style>
+  .hello {
+    color: blue;
+    border: 1px solid blue;
+    font-size: 12px;
+  }
+  p {
+    font-size: 14px;
+  }
+</mj-style>
+```
